      "author": "overmoro",
      "description": "## Changes\n\n- **Countdown timer** - counts down from a configurable target duration (default 30 minutes). Warn and critical thresholds are now minutes remaining, not elapsed.\n- **Overtime** - when the countdown reaches zero it continues past with a + prefix (e.g. +01:23) and deep red colouring, distinct from the critical amber and red states.\n- **Three-state tap cycle** - tap cycles Idle > Running > Paused > Idle. No confirmation dialog. Running shows a subtle pulse; Paused dims the pill. A small hint label beneath the pill shows the available action.\n- **Landscape full-width** - in landscape orientation the content expands to fill the viewport with 6vw side margins. Portrait retains the readable column width.\n- **Larger timer pill** - font size and padding increased ~1.4x for comfortable readability and tap target on iPad.",
